**v0.0.0**
- Add initial design files

**v0.0.1**

CHANGED
- Replace original USB-C connector with new part that sits flush to board without cutout
- Add ESD protection to all connector nets
- Replace too-high capacitance ESD diodes on cell module and USB-C with high speed ESD diodes
- Configure JLC stackup JLC06161H-3313(Standard/Finished thickness1.54mm±10%)
	- Notably, change internal layer weight from 1oz to 0.5oz, including L5 power planes
- Change stackup from signal-ground-signal-power-ground-signal to signal-ground-signal-ground-power-signal for easier impedance matching
- Remove ground pours from top and bottom layers
- Clean up schematic symbols
- Properly compute and configure 100R, 90R differential pair geometries for L3, L1/L6
- Add impedance matching documentation
- Run DRC
- Add return vias
- Clean up silkscreen

